Package: ejabberd-mod-admin-extra
Architecture: any
Depends: ejabberd (>= 1:14.12), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Extra commands for ejabberdctl
 This package gives you extra commands for ejabberctl

Package: ejabberd-mod-muc-admin
Architecture: any
Depends: ejabberd (>= 1:14.12), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Extra commands for ejabberdctl for MUC-administration
 This package gives you extra commands for ejabberctl

#Package: ejabberd-mod-archive
#Architecture: any
#Depends: ejabberd (>= 1:14.12), ${misc:Depends}
#Description: Support for Message Archiving (XEP-0136)
# This module does support almost all the XEP-0136 version 0.6 except otr 
# (off-the-record).
# .
# Features
#  * Automatic archiving
#  * User may enable/disable automatic archiving for one contact or globally
#  * Manual archiving
#  * Retrieve or remove archive
#  * XEP-0059

#Package: ejabberd-mod-archive-sql
#Architecture: any
#Depends: ejabberd (>= 1:14.12), ${misc:Depends}, postgresql
#Description: Support for Message Archiving (XEP-0136) using PostgreSQL
# This module does support almost all the XEP-0136 version 0.6 except otr 
# (off-the-record) using PostgreSQL as backend.
# .
# Features
#  * Automatic archiving
#  * User may enable/disable automatic archiving for one contact or globally
#  * Manual archiving
#  * Retrieve or remove archive
#  * XEP-0059

#Package: ejabberd-mod-archive-odbc
#Architecture: any
#Depends: ejabberd (>= 1:14.12), ${misc:Depends}
#Description: Support for Message Archiving (XEP-0136) using MySQL/SQLite3 via ODBC
# This module does support almost all the XEP-0136 version 0.6 except otr 
# (off-the-record) using MySQL or SQLite3 via ODBC as backend.
# .
# Features
#  * Automatic archiving
#  * User may enable/disable automatic archiving for one contact or globally
#  * Manual archiving
#  * Retrieve or remove archive
#  * XEP-0059

#Package: ejabberd-mod-archive-webview
